  "content": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListSystems_ctl00_LabelName\"></span></p>\n<p><em>The Silence Between<br /></em></p>\n<table style=\"width: 99.1549%; height: 167px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 20.6042%; height: 18px;\">Source</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.6856%; height: 18px;\">&nbsp;CRB pg. 493</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 20.6042%; height: 18px;\">Alignment</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.6856%; height: 18px;\">&nbsp;CG</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 20.6042%; height: 18px;\">Portfolios</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.6856%; height: 18px;\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListDeities_ctl00_LabelName\">&nbsp;goddess of distance, silence, space<br /></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 20.6042%; height: 18px;\">Centers of Worship</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.6856%; height: 18px;\">-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 20.6042%; height: 18px;\">Symbol</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.6856%; height: 18px;\">-</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListDeities_ctl00_LabelName\">As @Compendium[sfrpg.setting.Jr4DAaJPRZYMAV1n]{Desna} is goddess of the stars, the Black Butterfly is goddess of the dark spaces between them. Sometimes called @Compendium[sfrpg.setting.Jr4DAaJPRZYMAV1n]{Desna's} Shadow, the Black Butterfly despises evil and teaches that in the silences between breaths and thoughts, one can see one&rsquo;s true nature.</span></p>",
